      passage: `<p>Although what we once knew about the Pleistocene epoch and the way hominids lived in it was ______, recent study of fossils&mdash;among them the remains of the individual called Petralona 1, unearthed in Greece in 1960&mdash;has sharpened our sense of what a single day in Petralona 1&rsquo;s life may have been like.</p>`,
